*Naterao* je sina da uči. (He forced his son to study.)

*Naterala* sam ga da se ispriča. (I forced him to apologize.)

Nisu *naterani* da se tu zadrže. (They were not forced to stay there.)

Moj otac me je *naterao* da se prijavim na konkurs. (My father forced me to apply for the competition.)

*Nateravao* me je da radim sve zadatke pre roka. (He kept forcing me to do all the assignments before the deadline.)

*Naterivanje* je dovelo do rasprave. (The pushing was leading to a dispute.)